Maintainer: Ali Sadeghi Aghili <alisadeghiaghili@gmail.com>
Description: A comprehensive R package for statistical distribution fitting that goes
    beyond basic parameter estimation. Provides advanced goodness-of-fit tests 
    (Kolmogorov-Smirnov, Anderson-Darling, Chi-Square, CramÃ©r-von Mises), 
    comprehensive diagnostics (multiple residual types, influence measures, outlier 
    detection), bootstrap confidence intervals (parametric, non-parametric, BCa), 
    and full multilingual support (English, Persian/Farsi, German). Features 
    human-readable outputs, parallel processing, production-ready code quality,
    and comprehensive test coverage (210+ tests).
